idea-plugin.description:
Adds <code>/*index*/</code> comments before each element in a C# array initializer, making it easier to track indexed placeholders for string.Format().<br><br>

<b>Example:</b>
<br>
<pre><code>
const string offerTemplate = @"Hello, {0}!
Here is your personal offer: buy {1} {2} - get {3} {2}.";

var args = new object[]
{
    /*0*/ user.GetPresentationName(locale),
    /*1*/ offer.BuyAmount.GetPresentationView(locale),
    /*2*/ offer.GetProductName(locale),
    /*3*/ offer.GetAmount.GetPresentationView(locale)
};

var text = string.Format(offerTemplate, args);
</code></pre>
